      "item": {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "id": "44c5202e340c6628",
        "text": "VON FOERSTER, Heinz, 2003. Ethics and Second-Order Cybernetics. In: VON FOERSTER, Heinz, Understanding Understanding. Online. New York, NY: Springer New York. p. 287–304. [Accessed 21 July 2022]. ISBN 978-0-387-95392-2. \n"
